# React Components

## Pattern
- Functional components with named exports
- Props interface above component: `interface FooProps { ... }`
- Use `'use client'` directive only when needed (hooks, events, browser APIs)
- Server components by default in `src/app/`

## Hooks
- Extract reusable logic into `src/hooks/`
- Use TanStack Query for async data (`useQuery`, `useMutation`)
- Use Wagmi hooks for on-chain reads (`useReadContract`, `useAccount`)

## State
- Local state: `useState` / `useReducer`
- Server state: TanStack Query
- Global: React Context in `src/context/`
- No Redux, no Zustand

## Error Boundaries
- Wrap pages with error boundaries
- Show user-friendly fallback, log details to console
